  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Salesperson",
  "description": "<p>Mofunland is a brain-training and puzzle-based learning playground, specialising in <strong>cubing, brain training, competitions, camps, and enrichment programmes</strong>.<br />We actively collaborate with <strong>enrichment centres, schools, academies, and education partners</strong> to deliver high-impact programmes for students across Singapore.</p><p>We are looking for a <strong>Sales Executive (Partnerships)</strong> who enjoys building relationships, exploring collaborations, and creating win-win partnerships in the education space.</p><h2>🎯 Key Responsibilities</h2><h3>🤝 Partnership & Collaboration Sales</h3><ul><li><p>Promote Mofunland’s services to:</p><ul><li><p>Enrichment centres</p></li><li><p>Tuition centres</p></li><li><p>Learning studios & academies</p></li><li><p>Education operators</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Initiate and manage B2B collaboration discussions:</p><ul><li><p>Programme partnerships</p></li><li><p>Workshops & camps</p></li><li><p>Revenue-sharing models</p></li><li><p>Co-branded events or competitions</p></li></ul></li></ul><h3>📞 Lead Generation & Outreach</h3><ul><li><p>Identify and approach potential partners via:</p><ul><li><p>Calls, emails, WhatsApp, LinkedIn, walk-ins</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Schedule meetings, presentations, and follow-ups</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain a pipeline of collaboration leads</p></li></ul><h3>🧠 Solution-Based Selling</h3><ul><li><p>Understand partner needs (space, students, revenue goals)</p></li><li><p>Propose suitable collaboration models:</p><ul><li><p>On-site programmes</p></li><li><p>Joint camps / holiday programmes</p></li><li><p>Trainer deployment</p></li><li><p>Event-based collaboration</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Customize proposals and pricing with internal team</p></li></ul><h3>📊 Relationship Management</h3><ul><li><p>Maintain long-term relationships with partners</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal operations, trainers, and marketing teams</p></li><li><p>Support onboarding of new partners</p></li></ul><h2>🧠 Requirements</h2><h3>✅ Must-Have</h3><ul><li><p>Experience in <strong>sales, partnerships, or business development</strong></p></li><li><p>Comfortable with <strong>B2B discussions</strong> and education-related services</p></li><li><p>Strong communication & presentation skills</p></li><li><p>Self-driven, organised, and target-oriented</p></li><li><p>Able to handle follow-ups and basic reporting</p></li></ul><h3>👍 Nice-to-Have</h3><ul><li><p>Experience in <strong>education / enrichment / tuition industry</strong></p></li><li><p>Existing network of enrichment centres</p></li><li><p>Familiar with Singapore education landscape</p></li><li><p>Able to present proposals confidently to owners / principals</p></li></ul><h2>💡 Personality Fit </h2><ul><li><p>Relationship-focused (not pushy hard sell)</p></li><li><p>Confident but respectful</p></li><li><p>Able to explain value clearly to non-technical partners</p></li><li><p>Comfortable hearing “not now” and following up professionally</p></li></ul><h2>🎯 KPIs (Example)</h2><ul><li><p>Number of new enrichment centre partnerships</p></li><li><p>Number of meetings arranged</p></li><li><p>Conversion rate from discussion → collaboration</p></li><li><p>Revenue generated from partnerships</p></li></ul><p></p><h2>💰 Salary & Commission</h2><ul><li><p>Basic salary + commission+Reward+Performance bonus</p></li></ul>",
